rements private label funds we offer certain institutional clients the possibility of setting up funds under their own name with either switzerland or luxemburg as a domicile sarasin investment foundation founded in 99 the sast investment foundation mainly serves small and midsized pension funds vested benefits foundations pillar a foundations and other company pension schemes structured products bank j safra sarasin’s structured products can provide capital protection a fixed source of income or higher than average returns they are made up of a traditional underlying financial instrument for example equities fixed income securities and derivatives usually options alternative investments as investor you expect higher returns for the investment risk taken bank j safra sarasin’s alternative investments help you achieve this goal we offer investment products whose performance is largely independent from financial markets such as equities and bonds bank j safra sarasin’s specialists are happy to offer advice and explain how alternative investments – hedge funds private equity and commodities – can enhance your portfolio products direct access to product web sitesfundfinderderivatives to the top × welcome to your eservices carry out banking transactions any time  simply securely and quicklylogin eservices × welcome to your online services carry out banking transactions any time  simply securely and quicklylogin online services × disclaimer you are about to leave the website of bank j safra sarasin ltd please be aware that the external sites of third parties linked to our website are not under our control and as such not verified by us we are therefore in no way liable for their legal compliance andor content and expressly draw your attention to the fact that the views and opinions expressed and any advice subsequently offered are not those of bank j safra sarasin ltd please click on the following link to leave the website of j safra sarasin group if you do not wish to le